main event: A blue light object was observed in the sky in Chatham, New Jersey on September 12, 1964.
interesting points: The object was visible for approximately 15-20 minutes,The weather was clear with a 3/4 full moon,The object appeared to have a pulsating trail and moved strangely,There was no physical evidence collected after the observation,The conclusion of the report stated insufficient data for evaluation.
sighted object: a blue light with a slight trail
witness description: A 15-year-old who was outside talking when he noticed the object in the sky.
